@node main "IconAuthorDemo v1.06 - ® K÷ssi 92"

           This is the tool I've missed until I did it by myself.

                             You will like it !

                            What is it good for ?

 IconAuthor  can  transform  IFF  images  or brushes into resized 2-BitPlane
 brushes  or  iconfiles  that  match  the WorkBench2.0 colors.  The image is
 rasterized to keep as much details as possible.

 IconAuthor  offers basic drawingtools to edit the rendered image, including
 the possibility to insert text.

                           Where is the problem ?

                  IconAuthor needs Am*gaDOS 2.0 ! U2 \8-( ?

